esign-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-25-810x532.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist kitchen with wooden cabinets, a large window, and a white island with two stools.\" width=\"810\" height=\"532\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-25-810x532.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-25-800x526.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-25-768x505.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-25-385x252.jpg 385w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-25.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAt the west end of the garage, an open-air kitchen and dining area is sheltered by soaring cedar ceilings and solid brick walls. A wide opening frames the mountain views, while a brick screen on the south side provides privacy and filtered sunlight. A discreet slot in the masonry helps release built-up heat in summer. Inside, the glass entry hall leads to the main living area, reached through a wooden partition that subtly directs movement. This central living space rises to the full height of the gabled structure, where horizontal openings give access to terraces. Overhead, a lime-plastered vaulted ceiling enhances the interior’s quiet character.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=565373\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-565373\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-26-810x1227.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist kitchen with light wood cabinets, white countertops, an induction cooktop, and a large window offering a view of greenery. A small square window is near the ceiling.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1227\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-26-810x1227.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-26-800x1212.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-26-768x1163.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-26-1014x1536.jpg 1014w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-26.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=565371\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-565371\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-29-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist interior with light wood paneling, a white countertop, and a staircase with wooden steps.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-29-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-29-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-29-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-29-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-29.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=565375\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-565375\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-24-810x544.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with high ceiling, wood paneling, large windows, gray flooring, white sectional sofa, leather chair, and a black wood-burning stove centered on the back wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"544\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-24-810x544.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-24-800x538.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-24-768x516.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-24.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThroughout, a restrained palette of white oak, lime plaster, and stone maintains a calm atmosphere. Exterior materials such as brick, stone, steel, and cedar were chosen for durability, with deep openings, masonry pillars, and stone walls imparting a sense of permanence.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=565370\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-565370\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-31-810x557.jpg\" alt=\"A minimalist bedroom with a wooden closet wall, a glimpse of a modern bathroom featuring a white freestanding bathtub and a mirror in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"557\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-31-810x557.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-31-800x550.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-31-768x528.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-31.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=565376\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-565376\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-23-810x545.jpg\" alt=\"Modern living room with a leather chair, large sliding glass doors, and a view of green hills and trees. A gray floor and light wood wall complete the minimalist design.\" width=\"810\" height=\"545\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-23-810x545.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-23-800x538.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-23-768x517.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-23.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=565369\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-565369\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-35-810x1199.jpg\" alt=\"A bright interior staircase with wooden steps leads down to a large window overlooking a green lawn and trees. The walls are white, and there\u0026#39;s a glass railing on one side.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1199\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-35-810x1199.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-35-800x1184.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-35-768x1136.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-35-1038x1536.jpg 1038w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/12/deslauriershouse-paulbernierarchitecte-35.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more information, visit \u003ca href=\"https://www